edu.upc.etsetb.arqsoft.spreadsheet.usecases.marker

Interface ISpreadsheetFactoryForChecker


  • public interface ISpreadsheetFactoryForChecker
    Author:
    Juan Carlos Cruellas at Universidad Politécnica de Cataluña An interface that you MUST fill for ENCAPSULATING YOUR OWN PROCESS FOR creating the whole framework of objects that your code needs, and create your initial spreadsheet, your own controller and the class that implements the ISpreadsheetControllerForChecker interface, so that once finalized the execution of the static method createSpreadsheetController(), everything is ready for invoking the methods of the object implementing the ISpreadsheetControllerForChecker interface and starting setting contents in the spreadsheet cells and start checking results and marking your code
